---

<Layout
  title="Our Philosophy | Holistic Dental Care | Central Dentist Dallas"
  description="Discover our holistic approach to dentistry - treating the whole person, using biocompatible materials, and addressing root causes for optimal oral and systemic health."
>
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <PageHero
    title="Our Holistic Philosophy"
    subtitle="Treating the Whole Person, Not Just Teeth"
    backgroundImage="/images/services/abstract-white-texture.jpg"
    variant="standard"
    breadcrumbs={[
      { label: 'Our Philosophy', href: '#' }
    ]}
  />

  <!-- Core Philosophy Section - White Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary text-center mb-8">
            Dentistry That Honors Your Whole Body
          </h2>
        </BlurFade>

        <BlurFade delay={200}>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-dark">
              At Central Dentist, we believe your mouth is the gateway to your overall health. What happens
              in your oral cavity doesn't stay there â€“ it affects your entire body. This understanding drives
              our holistic approach to dentistry, where we consider not just your teeth and gums, but your
              complete wellness journey.
            </p>

            <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-dark">
              Traditional dentistry often treats symptoms. We dig deeper to find root causes. A cavity isn't
              just a hole to fill â€“ it's a sign that something in your body's ecosystem needs attention.
              Maybe it's nutrition, maybe it's pH balance, maybe it's airway issues affecting your sleep.
              We look at the whole picture to help you achieve lasting oral and systemic health.
            </p>

            <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-dark">
              Every material we use, every treatment we recommend, and every protocol we follow is chosen
              with your total health in mind. We're not just fixing problems â€“ we're partnering with your
              body's natural healing abilities to create sustainable wellness.
            </p>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Principles Section - Gray Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary">Our Core Principles</h2>
            <p class="text-section-subheader">The foundation of our holistic approach</p>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
          {principles.map((principle, index) => (
            <BlurFade delay={200 + index * 100}>
              <Card variant="bordered" class="h-full">
                <div class="p-8">
                  <div class={`w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r ${principle.gradient} flex items-center justify-center mb-6`}>
                    <span class="text-white text-2xl">{principle.icon}</span>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-card-header text-header-primary mb-4">{principle.title}</h3>
                  <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">
                    {principle.description}
                  </p>
                </div>
              </Card>
            </BlurFade>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What Makes Us Different Section - White Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary">
              What Makes Our Approach Different
            </h2>
            <p class="text-section-subheader">
              Comprehensive care that goes beyond traditional dentistry
            </p>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
          {differentiators.map((item, index) => (
            <BlurFade delay={200 + index * 100}>
              <div class="text-center">
                <h3 class="text-card-header text-header-secondary mb-4">{item.title}</h3>
                <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">
                  {item.description}
                </p>
              </div>
            </BlurFade>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Oral-Systemic Connection Section - Gray Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h2 class="text-section-header text-header-primary">
              The Oral-Systemic Connection
            </h2>
            <p class="text-section-subheader">
              Understanding how oral health impacts your entire body
            </p>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>

        <BlurFade delay={200}>
          <Card variant="bordered">
            <div class="p-8">
              <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-dark mb-8">
                Research consistently shows connections between oral health and systemic conditions. By addressing
                oral health holistically, we're not just protecting your teeth â€“ we're supporting your entire body's wellness.
              </p>

              <div class="space-y-4">
                {connections.map((item) => (
                  <div class="flex items-start">
                    <span class="text-xl mr-3" style="color: #a6b443;">â†’</span>
                    <div class="text-body-regular text-gray-dark">
                      <strong>{item.system}:</strong> {item.connection}
                    </div>
                  </div>
                ))}
              </div>
            </div>
          </Card>
        </BlurFade>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Quote Section - White Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <blockquote class="text-xl md:text-2xl italic text-gray-dark mb-4" style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
            "The mouth is the gateway to the body. A healthy mouth equals a healthy body."
          </blockquote>
          <p class="text-body-regular text-gray-medium">
            â€“ Dr. Jill Ombrello, Founder of Central Dentist
          </p>
        </BlurFade>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA Section - Blue Gradient Background -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20" style="background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #0099ba, #006786);">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 md:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <BlurFade delay={100}>
          <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-normal text-white mb-4"
              style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;">
            Experience Holistic Dentistry
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/90 mb-8" style="font-family: 'Geist', sans-serif;">
            Ready to experience dentistry that considers your whole health? Schedule a consultation to
            discuss how our holistic approach can benefit you and your family.
          </p>
          <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="px-8 py-3 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#a6b443] to-[#c7cd85] text-white rounded-full font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:from-[#8fa339] hover:to-[#a6b443] hover:shadow-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center"
              style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;"
            >
              Schedule Consultation
            </a>
            <a
              href="tel:214-368-0900"
              class="px-8 py-3 bg-white border-2 rounded-full font-semibold transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-lg inline-flex items-center justify-center"
              style="font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; color: #0099ba; border-color: white;"
              onmouseover="this.style.backgroundColor='#006786'; this.style.color='white'; this.style.borderColor='#006786';"
              onmouseout="this.style.backgroundColor='white'; this.style.color='#0099ba'; this.style.borderColor='white';"
            >
              <svg class="mr-2 w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z" />
              </svg>
              Call (214) 368-0900
            </a>
          </div>
        </BlurFade>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
